==专业评价==
《谁陷害了兔子罗杰》上映后获得了评论界的好评，根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的66篇专业评论文章，其中64篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”高达97%，平均得分8.4分（满分10分）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/who_framed_roger_rabbit/ | title = Who Framed Roger Rabbit | work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher = Flixster | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-05-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130515195934/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/who_framed_roger_rabbit/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。而另一家综合评论收集网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]则根据其收集到的15篇评论文章给出了83分（满分100分）的平均分<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/who-framed-roger-rabbit/critic-reviews |title=Who Framed Roger Rabbit (1988): Reviews |work=Metacritic |publisher=CBS Interactive |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040311230559/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/whoframedrogerrabbit/ |archivedate=2004-03-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》影评专栏作家[[罗杰·艾伯特|罗杰·艾伯特]]给影片正面评价，预期其将会有“万金难买[[口口相传|口口相传]]的影响力。这部电影不但是娱乐上的杰作，更表现出了突破性的精湛工艺”<ref>{{cite news | author = Roger Ebert | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/who-framed-roger-rabbit-1988 | title = Who Framed Roger Rabbit | work = Chicago Sun-Times | date = 1988-06-22 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-06-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130602193603/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/who-framed-roger-rabbit-1988 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的简妮特·玛斯琳曾评价道，“虽然这并非首次真人与动画角色一起在大银幕上演出，但却是第一次让之看上去这么真实”<ref>{{cite news |author=Janet Maslin |title=Who Framed Roger Rabbit |work=The New York Times |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=940DEFDD163FF931A15755C0A96E948260 |date=1988-06-22 |accessdate=2013-05-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021124312/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=940DEFDD163FF931A15755C0A96E948260 |archivedate=2013-10-21 }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的德森·汤姆森认为《谁陷害了兔子罗杰》 是“天才们的伟大合作。泽米基斯拥有迪斯尼公司热心的支持，制片人史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格的拉动，华纳兄弟公司的祝福，加拿大动画设计师理查德·威廉姆斯的墨水和纸张，梅尔·布兰克的嗓音，杰夫瑞·普莱斯和彼得·S·西曼机智风趣而又疯狂的剧本，[[乔治·卢卡斯|乔治·卢卡斯]]的工业光魔公司和鲍勃·霍斯金斯的滑稽表演”<ref>{{cite news | author = Desson Thomson | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/whoframedrogerrabbitpghowe_a0b16f.htm | title = Who Framed Roger Rabbit | work = The Washington Post | date = 1988-06-24 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2012-11-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121111130734/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/whoframedrogerrabbitpghowe_a0b16f.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。不过，《[[时代周刊|时代周刊]]》的理查德·科里斯对电影给出了褒贬不一的评价。“开场的动画镜头都还好，不过有点太好了，开场这一段镜头比整部电影的层次都要高了。”他也对片中向美国动画工业[[致敬|致敬]]的部分感到很厌烦<ref>{{cite news | author = Richard Corliss | title = Creatures of A Subhuman Species | url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,967766,00.html | format = Registration required to read article | work = Time | date = 1988-06-27 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-05-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130524121024/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,967766,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

===奖项===
