Hollywood Foreign Press Association | accessdate = 2013-05-27 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，并获[[尼克频道儿童选择奖|尼克频道儿童选择奖]]最受欢迎电影奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1989-hugo-awards/ |work=The Hugo Awards |title=1989 Hugo Awards |accessdate=2013-05-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612033831/http://www.thehugoawards.org/hugo-history/1989-hugo-awards/ |archivedate=2010-06-12 }}</ref>。

