==影响==
[[File:Mickey-mouse-bugs-bunny-113.jpg|thumb]]和[[米老鼠|米老鼠]]首次出现在了一个镜头中]]
《谁陷害了兔子罗杰》重新引起了人们对美国动画黄金时代的兴趣，让现代动画开始进入高速的发展时期<ref name="Gore">{{cite book | author = Chris Gore | title = The 50 Greatest Movies Never Made | url = https://archive.org/details/50greatestmovies00gore |date = 1999-7| publisher = St. Martin's Press | location = New York City | chapter = Roger Rabbit Two: The Toon Platoon | pages = [https://archive.org/details/50greatestmovies00gore/page/165 165]–168 | isbn = 0-312-20082-X}}</ref>。1991年，[[華特迪士尼幻想工程|华特迪士尼幻想工程公司]]开始在位于加利福尼亚州[[阿纳海姆_(加利福尼亚州)|阿纳海姆]]的[[迪斯尼乐园|迪斯尼乐园]]开发{{link-en|米老鼠动画城|Mickey's Toontown}}，这个动画城在本片中出现过的那个动画人物居住的“动画城”的翻版，其中还有一条名叫{{link-en|兔子罗杰的动画旋转|Roger Rabbit's Car Toon Spin}}的游乐设施<ref name="Williams" />{{rp|88}}。

影片之后还后续拍摄了三部动画短片，分别是在《{{link-en|亲爱的，我把孩子缩小了|Honey, I Shrunk the Kids}}》之前放映的《Tummy Trouble》，与《[[迪克·特雷西|至尊神探]]》一起放映的"Roller Coaster Rabbit"以及包含在《{{link-en|幻象大猎杀|A Far Off Place}}》中的《Trail Mix-Up》<ref>{{cite news | author = Aljean Harmetz | title = Marketing Magic, With ''Rabbit'', for Disney Films | work = New York Times | date = 1989-07-19 }}</ref><ref name="Maria">{{cite news | author = Maria Eftimiades | title = It's Heigh Ho, as Disney Calls the Toons to Work | work =New York Times | date = 1990-04-29 }}</ref>，而在这以前，迪斯尼公司已经有24年没有推出过面向电影观众的动画短片了。此外，影片还衍生出了一些漫画书、电子和电脑游戏作品，甚至还有由日本发行的游戏<ref name="Maria" />。

===争议===
电影的[[镭射影碟|镭射影碟]]发行后，《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》杂志于1994年率先报道称，有人在电影的部分镜头中发现了兔子罗杰的妻子杰茜卡的短暂裸露镜头。只是这些镜头在电影每秒24帧的正常播放速度下是无法发现的，而镭射影碟播放机则允许用机一帧一帧地步进来“发现”这样的内容。不过无论如何设计师是否是故意要画出动画角色的裸露形象这点仍然无法确定<ref name="Snopes1">{{cite web|url=http://snopes.com/disney/films/jessica.asp#add|title=Naked Jessica Rabbit|publisher=Snopes.com|accessdate=2013-05-27}}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://variety.com/1994/voices/columns/jessica-rabbit-revealed-119154/ | title = Jessica Rabbit revealed | work = Variety | date = 1994-03-14 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-04-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130412045520/http://variety.com/1994/voices/columns/jessica-rabbit-revealed-119154/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。许多零售商表示，自从包括[[有线新闻网|有线新闻网]]和多家报纸在内的媒体报道了这一情况后，本片的镭射影碟刚一上架马上就被抢购一空<ref>{{cite news | author = Adam Sandler | url = http://variety.com/1994/digital/news/rabbit-frames-feed-flap-119269/ | title = ''Rabbit'' frames feed flap | work = Variety | date = 1994-03-16 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-05-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130518205502/http://variety.com/1994/digital/news/rabbit-frames-feed-flap-119269/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一位迪斯尼公司的高管对《综艺》的报道这样回应道：“这些人的生活得空虚到什么程度才会发现这样的事情。我们可能永远都不会知道这些，这只是个愚蠢的噱头。与此同时，对这种事儿人们也应该要有点幽默感。”<ref>{{cite news | author = Michael Fleming | url = http://variety.com/1994/voices/columns/kopelson-does-major-defense-spending-119278/ | title = Kopelson does major ''Defense'' spending | work = Variety | date = 1994-03-17 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131023100518/http://variety.com/1994/voices/columns/kopelson-does-major-defense-spending-119278/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

其它一些导致争议的镜头还包括娃娃哈曼比中指，或是经过一位女性裙子下时流出口水的镜头<ref name="Snopes1" /><ref name="Variety" />。而在唐老鸭和达菲鸭一起出现的一个镜头中，据说唐老鸭在大声咆哮胡言乱语的过程中称达菲鸭是“愚蠢该死的黑鬼”，然而这其实只是个误会，剧本中这一句台词实际上是“死倔死硬的傻瓜”<ref name="Schweizer">{{cite book|last=Schweizer|coauthors=Peter & Rochelle|title= Disney: The Mouse Betrayed.|url=https://archive.org/details/disneymousebetra00schw|publisher=Regnery|year=1998|pages=[https://archive.org/details/disneymousebetra00schw/page/143 143]& 144|isbn=0-89526-387-4}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://snopes.com/disney/films/donald.asp|title=Quacking Wise}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Smith|first=Dave|title=Disney A to Z: The Official Encyclopedia}}</ref>。

===法律争议===
2001年，小说《谁审查了兔子罗杰》的作者格瑞·K·沃尔夫向法院起诉华特迪士尼公司声称该公司拖欠了他应得的商品销售和“总收入”的特许权使用费。2002年，法院驳回了沃尔夫的诉状，认为总收入只是指迪斯尼公司的现金收益。沃尔夫不服于是提出上诉，并请来专家证人指出根据娱乐行业的习惯，所谓“总收入”并不仅仅包含现金收益，而应该有更广泛的解读。2004年1月，加利福尼亚州上诉法院裁决原名胜诉，推翻了原本的判决并发回重审<ref>{{cite news |author=Paul Sweeting |title=Disney, ''Roger Rabbit'' author in spat |work=Video Business |date=2004-02-05 |url=http://www.videobusiness.com/article/CA614737.html |accessdate=2013-05-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20020201210442/http://www.videobusiness.com/article/CA614737.html |archivedate=2002-02-01 }}</ref>。在2005年3月的听证会上，沃尔夫估算称迪斯尼公司欠他700万美元。对方律师则声称迪斯尼公司不但不欠原告分毫，并且由于之前会计在案前统计时出现失误，沃尔夫实际上反而还欠迪斯尼公司50万至100万美元<ref>{{cite news |author=Jesse Hiestand |url=http://www.allbusiness.com/services/motion-pictures/4903763-1.html |title=Roger Rabbit Animated In Court |work=AllBusiness.com |date=2005-03-22 |accessdate=2013-05-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108212723/http://www.allbusiness.com/services/motion-pictures/4903763-1.html |archivedate=2009-01-08 }}</ref>。

===续集===
由于《谁陷害了兔子罗杰》在商业和评论上均获得了很大的成功，迪斯尼公司和史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格都认为应该拍摄一部续集。纳特·默尔汀写下了一个以1941年为时代背景的前传故事，标题为《兔子罗杰：动画小队》。与之前的电影类似，这个前传中也有许多动画角色客串出镜。故事以兔子罗杰早年生活在[[美国中西部|美国中西部]]的农场中开始<ref name="Gore"/>，他与一位叫里奇·达文波特的人类一起四处旅行来寻找自己的母亲，路上遇上了一位正在努力拼搏中的好莱坞女演员杰茜卡·克鲁帕尼克（之后嫁给了罗杰）。之后罗杰和里奇被征兵入伍，而杰茜卡则被绑架，并被迫在广播中对[[纳粹德国|纳粹德国]]进行宣传。罗杰和里奇必须深入纳粹横行的欧洲去拯救杰茜卡，不过幸好他们也有军队中其他众动画人物所组成小队的支援。成功挫败纳粹的阴谋并救出杰茜卡后，罗杰和里奇获得了[[好莱坞大道|好莱坞大道]]游行的热烈欢迎，罗杰也终于与自己的父母团聚，原来他的爸爸正是[[兔八哥|兔八哥]]<ref name="Gore" /><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.filmbuffonline.com/FBOLNewsreel/wordpress/2005/08/07/script-review-roger-rabbit-ii-the-toon-platoon/ | title = Script Review: Roger Rabbit II: Toon Platoon | work = FilmBuffOnline.com | accessdate = 2012-09-07 | archive-date = 2012-11-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121116205015/http://www.filmbuffonline.com/FBOLNewsreel/wordpress/2005/08/07/script-review-roger-rabbit-ii-the-toon-platoon/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

默尔汀之后将剧本的标题改成了《谁发现了兔子罗杰》，但斯皮尔伯格由于之前拍摄了以严肃角度反映纳粹对[[犹太人大屠杀|犹太人大屠杀]]的电影《[[辛德勒的名单|辛德勒的名单]]》，认为自己不适合参加一部以讽刺角度来看待纳粹的电影制作，他因此退出了这个项目<ref>{{cite news | author = Steve Daly | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20192040,00.html | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2008-04-16 | title = Steven Spielberg and George Lucas: The Titans Talk! | accessdate = 2013-05-17 | archive-date = 2013-05-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130501223421/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20192040,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="world">{{cite news | author = Martin "Dr. Toon" Goodman | title = Who Screwed Roger Rabbit? | work = Animation World Magazine | url = http://www.awn.com/articles/drtoon/who-screwed-roger-rabbit | date = 2003-04-03 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2013-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130129135721/http://www.awn.com/articles/drtoon/who-screwed-roger-rabbit | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1997年，迈克尔·艾思纳委托谢里·斯通和迪安娜·奥利弗来改写剧本。他们虽保留了罗杰寻找母亲的情节，但改写了罗杰意外成为[[百老汇|百老汇]]和好莱坞明星的设定。迪斯尼对新的剧本表示满意，并请[[阿兰·门肯|阿兰·门肯]]为电影谱写5首歌曲并担任执行制片人<ref name="world" />，其中一首歌《这只会发生在电影中》（This Only Happens in the Movies）于2008年录制发行<ref>{{cite news | url = http://broadwayworld.com/viewcolumn.cfm?colid=25560 | title = Kerry Butler's 'Faith, Trust and Pixie Dust' Set For May Release | work = Broadway World | date = 2008-02-28 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2008-05-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080501053752/http://broadwayworld.com/viewcolumn.cfm?colid=25560 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。艾瑞克·戈德伯格则担任续集的动画制作总监，并且已经开始重新设计罗杰的新形象<ref name="world" />。

虽然弗兰克·马歇尔和凯瑟琳·肯尼迪都决定继续出任制片人一职，但斯皮尔伯格正在创建[[梦工厂|梦工厂]]因此无意加入。1998年，剧组在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]的[[布埃纳文图拉湖_(佛罗里达州)|布埃纳文图拉湖]]拍摄了《谁发现了兔子罗杰》的样片，但由于其中电脑成像技术、传统动画工艺和真人演出结合的效果欠佳，迪斯尼公司很不满意。第二次拍摄的样片将所有动画人物都通过电脑成像进行转换，但这也导致影片的项目预算超过1亿美元，因此整个计划被搁置，艾思纳干脆认为最好还是取消这部电影<ref name="world" />。2003年3月，制片人唐·海恩表示，“不要预期《兔子罗杰》的续集会很快出来，今天的动画已经彻底为计算机所征服，传统的动画技术已经过时了。”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2003-03-26-rabbit_x.htm | title = Don't expect a ''Rabbit'' sequel | work = USA Today | date = 2003-03-26 | accessdate = 2013-05-27 | archive-date = 2012-11-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121104141721/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2003-03-26-rabbit_x.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

2007年12月，马歇尔表示自己仍然有意参与续集的制作工作<ref name="Frank">{{cite news | url = http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/12/11/roger-rabbit-sequel-still-in-the-offing-stay-tooned-says-producer/ | title = ''Roger Rabbit'' Sequel Still In The Offing? Stay Tooned, Says Producer | author = Shawn Adler | date = 2007-09-11 | work = MTV Movies Blog | accessdate = 2008-11-04 | archive-date = 2012-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017173326/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2007/12/11/roger-rabbit-sequel-still-in-the-offing-stay-tooned-says-producer/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，2009年4月，泽米基斯也表示自己仍然有兴趣<ref>{{cite news|author=Eric Ditzian|title=Robert Zemeckis ‘Buzzing’ About Second ‘Roger Rabbit’ Movie|work=MTV Movies Blog|date=2009-04-29|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/04/29/exclusive-robert-zemeckis-buzzing-about-second-roger-rabbit-movie/|accessdate=2013-05-27|archive-date=2012-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627064600/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/04/29/exclusive-robert-zemeckis-buzzing-about-second-roger-rabbit-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并表示前集的两位编剧杰夫瑞·普莱斯和彼得·S·西曼也正在编写新的剧本。他还表示电影中的动画角色将使用传统的2D技术，其他人物则会应用动画捕捉技术<ref>{{cite web |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/11/03/exclusive-robert-zemeckis-indicates-hell-use-performance-capture-and-3-d-in-roger-rabbit-sequel/ |title=EXCLUSIVE: Robert Zemeckis Indicates He’ll Use Performance-Capture And 3-D In ‘Roger Rabbit’ Sequel |publisher=Moviesblog.mtv.com |date= |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archive-date=2010-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101103072903/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/11/03/exclusive-robert-zemeckis-indicates-hell-use-performance-capture-and-3-d-in-roger-rabbit-sequel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过到了2010年，泽米基斯又表示续集中虽然会像前传那样使用2D技术制作和拍摄，但动画角色的光影效果等还是会使用数字技术来进行完善<ref>{{cite web |url=http://toontownantics.blogspot.com/2010/07/roger-rabbit-2-in-3d.html |title=Toontown Antics - Roger Rabbit's adventures in real and animated life: Roger Rabbit 2 – In 3D? |publisher=Toontownantics.blogspot.com |date=2010-07-20 |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archive-date=2013-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003162428/http://toontownantics.blogspot.com/2010/07/roger-rabbit-2-in-3d.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年唐·海恩也在接受《[[帝国杂志|帝国]]》采访时确定续集正在开发过程中。他对此说道，“是的，我对此没有任何评论。我彻底否认，不过好吧……要是你是一位粉丝的话，很快你就会非常、非常、非常高兴。”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=28191 |title=Exclusive: The Lion King To Go 3D! | Movie News | Empire |publisher=Empireonline.com |date= |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021034315/http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=28191 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年，鲍勃·霍斯金斯也表示自己仍然有意出演同一角色<ref>HeyUGuys.Twitter.September 2010</ref>，不过由于2011年他被诊断出患有[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]，他在2012年退出了演艺圈<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.itv.com/news/update/2012-08-08/bob-hoskins-retires-from-acting/ |title=Bob Hoskins retires from acting |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006123334/http://www.itv.com/news/update/2012-08-08/bob-hoskins-retires-from-acting/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。马修尔确定这部续集剧情上是一部前传，并且剧本已经基本上完成<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collider.com/frank-marshall-roger-rabbit-2-sequel-bourne-legacy/187006/ |title=Frank Marshall Talks WHO FRAMED ROGER RABBIT 2 Sequel, THE BOURNE LEGACY, THE GOONIES 2, More |publisher=Collider |accessdate=2013-05-27 |archive-date=2013-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121153809/http://collider.com/frank-marshall-roger-rabbit-2-sequel-bourne-legacy/187006/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2012年上映电影《[[迫降航班|迫降航班]]》的首映式上接受采访时，泽米基斯表示虽然霍斯金斯退休了，但续集仍然是有希望推出的，剧本已经送交迪斯尼公司高管等待批准<ref>{{cite web|last=Fischer|first=Russ|title=Despite Bob Hoskins’ Retirement, the ‘Roger Rabbit’ Sequel is Still Possible|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/despite-bob-hoskins-retirement-the-roger-rabbit-sequel-is-still-possible/|publisher=SlashFilm/Film|accessdate=2013-05-27|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523031138/http://www.slashfilm.com/despite-bob-hoskins-retirement-the-roger-rabbit-sequel-is-still-possible/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===兔子罗杰舞===
“兔子罗杰”在1990年代早期成为了一种流行舞步<ref>For example, fitness expert Monica Brant verifies her efforts to learn the dance in the 1990s in Monica Brant, ''Monica Brant's Secrets to Staying Fit and Loving Life'' (Sports Publishing LLC, 2005), [http://books.google.com/books?id=_-XovLHmb5EC&pg=PA4&dq=%22The+Roger+Rabbit+(dance)%22&ei=hTMbSYy8PIjUMpDrye8N North Carolina Tar Heels Where Have You Gone - Scott Fowler] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=_-XovLHmb5EC&pg=PA4&dq=%22The+Roger+Rabbit+(dance)%22&ei=hTMbSYy8PIjUMpDrye8N |date=20130613155302 }}.</ref><ref>The dance is even used in the dedication of W. Michael Kelley, ''The Complete Idiot's Guide to Calculus'' (Alpha Books, 2002), [http://books.google.com/books?id=H-0L9Dxor6sC&pg=PR2&dq=%22The+Roger+Rabbit+(dance)%22&ei=hTMbSYy8PIjUMpDrye8N The Complete Idiot's Guide to Calculus] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=H-0L9Dxor6sC&pg=PR2&dq=%22The+Roger+Rabbit+(dance)%22&ei=hTMbSYy8PIjUMpDrye8N |date=20130615002516 }}.</ref>，这种舞蹈由于与电影中卡通人物的动作接近而得名。

